3.Form

Form SmartForm:

Form, FormItem, Collector, validators

Setter FormItem 

<Form>
  <FormItem
    field="name"
    onChange={val =>
      this.setState({
        formName: val
      })
    }
  >
    <Input />
  </FormItem>
  <Item show={this.state.formName === ""}>
    <FormItem field="age">
      <Input />
    </FormItem>
  </Item>
</Form>

=>

<SmartForm>
  {(data, renderItem, setItem) => (
    <Fragment>
      {renderItem(
        <FormItem field="name">
          <Input />
        </FormItem>
      )}
      <Item show={data.name === ""}>
        {renderItem(
          <FormItem field="age">
            <Input />
          </FormItem>
        )}
      </Item>
    </Fragment>
  )}
</SmartForm>
